      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.ABarray"
      },
      "sc:description": "Automated pipline to perform gene expression analysis for Applied Biosystems Genome Survey Microarray (AB1700) data format. Functions include data preprocessing, filtering, control probe analysis, statistical analysis in one single function. A GUI interface is also provided. The raw data, processed data, graphics output and statistical results are organized into folders according to the analysis settings used.",
